      <seg function="incipit" type="root-text"><milestone unit="main-text-area"/>
        <lg><l><lb n="1"/>Ulakam yāvaiyu muṟupayaṉ viḷaippā</l>
<l>ṉalakil cōti yaṇikiḷar tiruvuru</l>
<l>vuṇarvuyi reṉakkalan tuttamar nittar</l>
<l>kaṇamaka la<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><lb n="2" break="no"/>ta poṟkaviṉ patiniṉṟu</l>
<l>muravunīr vaḷaitta voṉpāṉuṭ ṭeṉpulap</l>
<l>paratakaṇṭattuṭ papaḻampati yeṉappukum</l>
<l>viṇṭo<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭa nivanta poḻilvaṭa vēṅkaṭan</l>
<l>teṇṭirai kaṟaṅkuteṉ kumariyeṉ ṟāyiṭai</l>                                           
<l>yamiḻtiṉum vāṉcuvait tākiya mummait</l>
<l>tamiḻ<lb n="4" break="no"/>teri pulamaic cāṉṟōr matikku</l>
<l>mutumoḻit teṇṭi mutaṉū laṇiyoṭum</l>
<l>putumoḻip pulavar puṇarttiya laṇiyaiyun</l>
<l>taṉātunu<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṇ ṇuṇarvāṟ ṟarupala vaṇiyaiyu</l>
<l>maṉātuṟat tokuttum vakuttum virittum</l>
<l>potuviyal poruṭtuccol laṇiyecca viyaleṉac</l>
          <l><lb n="6"/>caturpeṟa viraṇṭiṭan taḻīiya cārpeṉalāyk</l>
<l>kāriyatan taruḷkalaik kaṭaliyaṟ peyarpuṉain</l>
<l>tāriyar tuvaṉṟa vavaik<lb n="7" break="no"/>kaḷat turaittaṉaṉ</l>
<l>ciṟkuṇac cīni vātaṉi ṉaruḷā</l>
<l>ṉaṟporuṇ mūṉṟaiyu nalaṉuṟa vuṇarvōṉ</l>
<l>perunilam pukaḻtiru<lb n="8" break="no"/>k kurukaip perumā</l>
<l>ḷaruḷkuru kūrvaru maṉakaṉ ceḻuntēṉ</l>
<l>marukkamaḻ cīrakat tārvaṇi kaṉpukaḻt</l>
<l>tirukkuru kaipperu māḷka<lb n="9" break="no"/>vi rāy</l>
<l>ṉaruṭkuṇat tuṭaṉvaḷar caṭaiyaṉ</l>
<l>poruṭṭoṭar navampuṇar pulamai yōṉē ~</l></lg></seg>
<seg function="incipit" type="commentary">Eṉpatu pāyiram ~ Ennūlu<lb n="10" break="no"/>raippiṉu mannūṟkup pāyiramuraitta nūlūraikka veṉpatu marapu ~ Eṉṉai ~ 
Āyira mukattā lakaṉṟa tāyiṉum
pāyira millatu paṉuva
  
  <pb n="[1]v" facs="4" break="no"/>
  
  <lb n="1"/>laṉṟē ~ Eṉa muṉṉōr kūṟiya muṟaimaiyāṉum ~ Innūluṭaiyārum ~ poṟipuṟavi<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>poru<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>yuṇarkkiṉun taṟciṟappu 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḷatē tantira meṉpa ~ Eṉpataṉālu muṇarka ~ Ippāyirattukkup poruṇ mēṟkā<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ṭutum ~ 
puṟavurai mukavurai puṇainturai tan<lb n="3"/>turai
patika nūṉmuka maṇinturai pāyiram ~
I<ex>taṉ</ex> ~ <ex>poru</ex>ḷ ~ Ivai yēḻum pāyirattutiṟkuk kāraṇappeyarā meṉṟavāṟu ~ 3 ~</seg> <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
          
