        <lb n="7"/>poruḷ pulavaṉ kūṟiya Avvava nūlukkuc ciṟanta poruḷkaḷāmeṉṉa vuṇarka <g ref="#pcl"/></seg> <seg function="colophon"><seg function="blessing">Āḻvār tiruvaṭikaḷē caraṇam ~</seg>
